            </seg>
          </p>
<p xml:id="KR3ej045_jc_000-d2.d10p6">
            <seg xml:id="KR3ej045_jc_000-d2.d10.p6s1">此方健脾平肝之聖藥<c n="，"/>
            </seg>
            <seg xml:id="KR3ej045_jc_000-d2.d10.p6s2">肝平則火散<c n="，"/>
            </seg>
            <seg xml:id="KR3ej045_jc_000-d2.d10.p6s3">脾健則風止<c n="，"/>
            </seg>
            <seg xml:id="KR3ej045_jc_000-d2.d10.p6s4">斷不可以風藥表散之也<c n="。"/>
            </seg>
          </p>

</div>
