            </seg>
            <seg xml:id="KR3ej045_jc_000-d2.d17.p4s9">水煎服<c n="。"/>
            </seg>
            <seg xml:id="KR3ej045_jc_000-d2.d17.p4s10">此心脾兩清之聖藥也<c n="，"/>
            </seg>
            <seg xml:id="KR3ej045_jc_000-d2.d17.p4s11">引火下行而府自去矣<c n="。"/>
            </seg>
          </p>

</div>
